                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-3">*All estimates assume 65% conversion efficiency (industry-standard conservative baseline). Premium GaN-based circuits at 85-92% efficiency deliver 20-30% more real-world charges. OEM brands using GaN circuits may claim higher numbers with supporting test data.</p>
                    </div>
